quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,91,"[JaŇčto kadi fii] oya [suddii…óo] reenunoo…óo farju makko on Men wutti e makko immorde e Fittaandu Amen, Men wa…ói mo kanko e ge…óaljo makko on Maande wonannde winndere nden"
  21,92,"Pellet, …óee mofte mo'on ko mofte goote, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on Rewee Lam"
  21,93,"∆Āe ta∆īi fiyaake ma…ď…ďe on hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, …ďe fow ko faade ka Am …ďe ruttoytoo"
  21,94,"Kala gollu…óo immorde e mo∆ī∆īu…ói …óin hara kanko ko o gom…óin…óo, dullugol alaa fii golle makko …óen, pellet, Menen Men winndanay mo"
  21,95,"No Harmani saare nde Men halki …óum, wonnde kam…ďe …ďe ruttataako [ton]"
  21,96,"Haa si udditoyaama Yaajuuja e Maajuuja, hara kam…ďe immorde e kala na…óel hi…ďe sortoo"
  21,97,"Fodoore Goongaare nden …ďadike, tawi kayre puttini gii…óe …ďen yeddu…ďe, […ďe wi'a:] \"Eeyoo bone amen, gom…óii men laatinoke e nder welsindaare immorde e …óu'um, ko woni, men laatike too√Īu…ďe"
  21,98,"Pellet, onon e ko rewoton kon gaanin Alla, ko on doccote Jahannama. Onon, ko on joloyay…ďe e magge"
  21,99,Sinndo …ďee laatinoke rewetee…ďe …ďe jolataano e magge. ∆Āe fow ma…ď…ďe ko …ďe luttintee…ďe e nder magge
  21,100,"No woodani …ďe e nder magge haraango, kam…ďe …ďe nanataa nder ton"
  21,101,"Pellet, …ďen …ďe mo∆ī∆īi …óin adanii …óum immorde ka Amen …ďen …óon ko …ďe wo…ó…óintintee…ďe gaayi magge"
